span>愛"},{"pid":"2e5dee08e978202642de778e3d964dfb9be728ab","tid":416304,"uid":133936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日子算係愛情劇咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎，仁醫更加唔算，係穿越劇先岩。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日子唔算咩...最後女主同男主講 叫佢努力追聽日既我 果度好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仁醫就係 由原本因為病床果個女人 (未婚妻定女朋友) 話醫學技術唔夠<br />\n<br />\n男主就返左去以前 同劇中女主角一齊經歷好多野 <br />\n<br />\n我自已睇落就算係一套好慘既愛情故仔 因為男主最後乜野都得唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本時間點既女朋友變到唔識佢 有個中意佢又肯為佢放棄好多野既古代女仔<br />\n<br />\n因為男主返左去 + 冇左記憶 = 乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71389faa25276f8099c3f85f33a1feaf767c87bb","tid":416304,"uid":133936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東京愛的故事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪91年果套"},{"pid":"16b343e0cd9ab55ab8e4a9bdf9d894330ac8118e","tid":416304,"uid":133936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講感動一定係求婚大作戰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你睇左LV或BL未？睇完你可能會改口</blockquote><br />\nBL？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBeautiful Life</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLV又係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ba46c059ac412ce1bd5bc618ff637ad83073b7","tid":416304,"uid":133936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日劇咁老土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal