s  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係幾好睇的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b06089bd69e26856143d002f9a137d1279852ed","tid":416304,"uid":1927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"魔女的條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd6d7d48368b85d141863d989afa315f483a35c","tid":416304,"uid":31979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在世界中心呼喊愛 大波遙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個中學睇喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529af7724d6894da172c7d521f384f1f0f9c3320","tid":416304,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"東愛我大大話話都睇左廿幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43709324beeddf5b065a9c74ed910c1e399d0da8","tid":416304,"uid":133936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"好多舊片都追曬<br />\n<br />\n有冇新少少既推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8105b5beef84e0e3d9a63d36bd7c74d162c0b69","tid":416304,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多舊片都追曬<br />\n<br />\n有冇新少少既推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今年嘅 我命中注定的人 深海魚男 加穗子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5a3e8e3fab08fd445a6bbcad4872c13ac6f8f4","tid":416304,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T21:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多舊片都追曬<br />\n<br />\n有冇新少少既推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今年嘅 我命中注定的人